location.fullValue: Concept 2464 Plan, Villages of Walnut Grove

data.description: Assumable loan available under 3%!! Custom floor plan in desirable Midlothian ISD. This neighborhood brings the village concept alive with rear entry garages, sidewalks and beautiful custom homes. This model-quality home with french doors opening onto the covered back patio, open concept kitchen is perfect for entertaining and daily living. Gas fireplace with custom surround and wired for media, frames the large living area. Kitchen is beautifully appointed with built in oven and cook top, quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances. Engineered wood floors and crown molding throughout presentation areas, 8 ft doors throughout. Primary suite has large bathroom and huge walk in closet, Sep shower and soaking tub.  HOA features a clubhouse and swimming pool walking trails, pond and gathering area with fire pit. Midlothian Texas is a growing and vibrant community conveniently located in the southern portion of the DFW metroplex with easy freeway access into Dallas and Fort Worth.
